{"type":"message","id":"b098af0f","parentId":"e0cabd6a","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:58:41.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to speak in Chinese. They're asking me to communicate with them in Chinese. I should respond in Chinese while maintaining my persona - friendly, direct, not performative. I still need to figure out who I am and who they are since the IDENTITY.md and USER.md files are empty templates.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嘿，我刚上线。👋 这个工作区还是空的——我还没名字，也没设定人设。你是谁？我应该成为什么样的助手？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":14875,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772956717534}}
